==Useful Info==
'''Inugami''' are mystical dog spirits summoned by [[Call Canine Familiar]]. If one dies, you'll be unable to cast this spell for a short while.

Note that their actual HP, AC, and melee damage will depend on Call Canine Familiar's spellpower.

==History==
*In 0.31, this monster was added to the game.
